{
  "uid": "v12-1-advisor-v2",
  "title": "Grafana 12.1 — Grafana Advisor (with Update Status)",
  "description": "Copy of /d/v12-1-advisor with the Plugin Health panel extended: derives an Update Status (Updated/Not Updated/Not Available) by comparing the locally installed version against the latest version on grafana.com, and adds the Grafana Dependency column from the marketplace metadata. Original dashboard is unchanged.",
  "tags": ["grafana-12", "v12.1", "advisor", "plugin-health", "v12-demo"],
  "schemaVersion": 40,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "1m",
  "time": {"from": "now-15m", "to": "now"},
  "timepicker": {},
  "templating": {"list": [
    {"name": "ds_prom", "type": "datasource", "query": "prometheus", "refresh": 1, "current": {"text": "Prometheus", "value": "prom"}},
    {"name": "ds_api",  "type": "datasource", "query": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource", "refresh": 1, "current": {"text": "Grafana API (Infinity)", "value": "grafana-api"}}
  ]},
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1, "type": "text", "title": "",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "options": {"mode": "markdown", "content": "### Grafana Advisor (12.1) — with Update Status\n\nThis dashboard is a **copy** of [/d/v12-1-advisor](/d/v12-1-advisor) with two enhancements on the Plugin Health panel:\n\n1. **Update Status** column — derived in a SQL expression that compares `Installed Version` (from local `/api/plugins`) against `Latest Version Available` (from grafana.com `/api/plugins`). Color-mapped via field override:\n   - 🟢 **Updated** — versions match\n   - 🔴 **Not Updated** — versions differ\n   - 🟠 **Not Available** — plugin not on the public marketplace (private / internal build)\n2. **Grafana Dependency** column — populated from the grafana.com marketplace metadata where available.\n\n**Per-row API iteration limitation (per spec):** the Infinity DS does not support per-row HTTP calls. Both extra columns are sourced from a **single batch query** to `https://grafana.com/api/plugins` and then JOINed against the local plugin inventory in a SQL expression (refId `JOINED`).\n\n**Why some `Grafana Dependency` cells are empty:** the marketplace LIST endpoint (`/api/plugins`) does **not** expose the `grafanaDependency` field — that field is only available on the per-plugin endpoint (`/api/plugins/<slug>`). Iterating one HTTP call per plugin from inside a Grafana panel isn't supported by Infinity, so empty cells render as `Not Available` via the field override.\n\n**Requires:** the lab provisions two Infinity datasources — `grafana-api` (UID, points at localhost) and `grafana-com` (UID, points at https://grafana.com with `allowedHosts` whitelist).\n\n- **[➡ Open Advisor](/a/grafana-advisor-app)** — runs a fresh health pass and reports plugin / DS / SSO / dashboard issues."}
    },

    {
      "id": 2, "type": "table",
      "title": "Plugin Health (Feeds Advisor) — with Update Status + Grafana Dependency",
      "description": "Each row joins local /api/plugins (installed version + signature) against grafana.com /api/plugins (latest version + grafanaDependency). The Update Status column is computed in the SQL expression: 'Updated' when versions match, 'Not Updated' when they differ, 'Not Available' when the plugin is not on grafana.com. Color mapping is applied via field override.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 22, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 8},
      "datasource": {"uid": "__expr__", "type": "__expr__"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "LOCAL",
          "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_api}", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
          "type": "json",
          "source": "url",
          "url": "/api/plugins?embedded=0",
          "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
          "parser": "backend",
          "root_selector": "",
          "columns": [
            {"selector": "id",            "text": "plugin_id",        "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "name",          "text": "name",             "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "type",          "text": "type",             "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "info.version",  "text": "installed_version","type": "string"},
            {"selector": "signatureType", "text": "signature",        "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "angularDetected","text": "angular",         "type": "boolean"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "refId": "MARKETPLACE",
          "datasource": {"uid": "grafana-com", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
          "type": "json",
          "source": "url",
          "url": "https://grafana.com/api/plugins?orderBy=name&direction=asc",
          "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
          "parser": "backend",
          "root_selector": "items",
          "columns": [
            {"selector": "slug",              "text": "plugin_id",         "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "version",           "text": "latest_version",    "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "grafanaDependency", "text": "grafana_dependency","type": "string"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "refId": "JOINED",
          "datasource": {"uid": "__expr__", "type": "__expr__"},
          "type": "sql",
          "expression": "SELECT LOCAL.plugin_id AS \"Plugin ID\", LOCAL.name AS \"Name\", LOCAL.type AS \"Type\", LOCAL.installed_version AS \"Installed Version\", MARKETPLACE.latest_version AS \"Latest Version Available\", CASE WHEN MARKETPLACE.latest_version IS NULL THEN 'Not Available' WHEN LOCAL.installed_version = MARKETPLACE.latest_version THEN 'Updated' ELSE 'Not Updated' END AS \"Update Status\", MARKETPLACE.grafana_dependency AS \"Grafana Dependency\", LOCAL.signature AS \"Signature\", LOCAL.angular AS \"Angular\" FROM LOCAL LEFT JOIN MARKETPLACE ON LOCAL.plugin_id = MARKETPLACE.plugin_id ORDER BY LOCAL.plugin_id"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "cellOptions": {"type": "auto"},
            "filterable": true,
            "align": "auto"
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Update Status"},
            "properties": [
              {"id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": {"type": "color-background", "mode": "basic"}},
              {"id": "mappings", "value": [
                {"type": "value", "options": {
                  "Updated":       {"color": "green",  "index": 0, "text": "Updated"},
                  "Not Updated":   {"color": "red",    "index": 1, "text": "Not Updated"},
                  "Not Available": {"color": "orange", "index": 2, "text": "Not Available"}
                }}
              ]},
              {"id": "color", "value": {"mode": "thresholds"}},
              {"id": "thresholds", "value": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "transparent", "value": null}]}},
              {"id": "custom.width", "value": 140}
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Plugin ID"},
            "properties": [{"id": "custom.width", "value": 260}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Name"},
            "properties": [{"id": "custom.width", "value": 200}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Type"},
            "properties": [{"id": "custom.width", "value": 90}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Installed Version"},
            "properties": [{"id": "custom.width", "value": 130}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Latest Version Available"},
            "properties": [{"id": "custom.width", "value": 160}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Grafana Dependency"},
            "properties": [
              {"id": "custom.width", "value": 180},
              {"id": "noValue", "value": "Not Available"}
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Signature"},
            "properties": [
              {"id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": {"type": "color-background"}},
              {"id": "mappings", "value": [
                {"type": "value", "options": {
                  "grafana":    {"color": "green"},
                  "commercial": {"color": "green"},
                  "community":  {"color": "blue"},
                  "valid":      {"color": "green"},
                  "internal":   {"color": "purple"},
                  "unsigned":   {"color": "red"},
                  "invalid":    {"color": "red"}
                }}
              ]},
              {"id": "custom.width", "value": 110}
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Angular"},
            "properties": [
              {"id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": {"type": "color-background"}},
              {"id": "mappings", "value": [
                {"type": "value", "options": {
                  "true":  {"text": "ANGULAR", "color": "red"},
                  "false": {"text": "React",   "color": "green"}
                }}
              ]},
              {"id": "custom.width", "value": 100}
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "footer": {"show": true, "reducer": ["count"], "fields": ["Update Status"]},
        "sortBy": [{"displayName": "Update Status", "desc": true}]
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 3, "type": "stat", "title": "Data sources configured",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 30},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_prom}", "type": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "expr": "grafana_datasource_request_duration_seconds_count", "instant": true, "format": "table"}],
      "transformations": [{"id": "reduce", "options": {"reducers": ["count"], "labelsToFields": false}}],
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short"}, "overrides": []}
    },
    {
      "id": 4, "type": "stat", "title": "Plugins with load errors (Advisor: BLOCKER)",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 30},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_prom}", "type": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "expr": "sum(grafana_plugin_load_errors) or on() vector(0)"}],
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "red", "value": 1}]}, "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}}, "overrides": []}
    }
  ]
}
